import React from "react";
import { Navbar,Container,NavDropdown,Collapse,Nav } from 'react-bootstrap';
const Navbars = () => {
    return ( 
        <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">


            <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
        


            <NavDropdown title="Diagnostic" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Brain-Tumor</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">
                Skin-Cancer
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Lung</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Divider />
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">
                Separated link
              </NavDropdown.Item>
            </NavDropdown>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
     );
}
 
export default Navbars;
